headline: Aon (AON) Q1 Earnings and Revenues Lag Estimates
summary: Aon (AON) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -6.13% and 2.63%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
